title: Forms to be furnished by director
context: §425-2 Forms to be furnished by director. The registration, annual and other statements required by this part shall be filed on forms to be furnished by the director of commerce and consumer affairs. [L 1969, c 247, pt of §1; am L 1980, c 270, §2; am L 1982, c 204, §8; am L 1983, c 124, §17]
